name: TRIQUETRA KNOT GIF - INVERTED TRIANGLE EDITION
description:
The triquetra is a triangular figure made up of three interlaced arcs. These interlaced arcs are composed of vesicae piscis lens shapes.

This specific triquetra knot is fairly rare as it's locked within a circle and inverted equilateral triangle. The shapes, collectively, all fit perfectly together.

It was built using geometric proofs and algebra and was completed on the 2nd May 2018.
